    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with no chips or scratches, and the interior still retains that new-car smell with absolutely no wear on the leather or upholstery. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as they did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle in pristine, collector-grade condition.",
